title: Jars of Clay - Redemption Songs - Ogg
description:
Jars of Clay&#039;s "Redemption Songs" album in Ogg format.
I did my best to tag it properly, but guest artists threw me off a bit. As long as parenthesis don&#039;t mess up your library it should be fine.
Have fun.

Tracks:

God Be Merciful to Me (Psalm 51)
I Need Thee Every Hour
God Will Lift Up Your Head
I&#039;ll Fly Away (Featuring Sarah Kelly)
Nothing But the Blood (Featuring The Blind Boys of Alabama)
Let Us Love and Sing and Wonder (Featuring Martin Smith of Delirious)
O Come and Mourn With Me Awhile
Hiding Place
Jesus, I Lift My Eyes
It Is Well With My Soul
On Jordan&#039;s Stormy Banks I Stand (Featuring The Blind Boys of Alabama)
Thy Lovely Source of True Delight
They Will Know We are Christians By Our Love

Not an album I really cared for, but maybe a &#039;Jars of Clay&#039; fan would like it.
Seed it or I&#039;ll stick a livewire up your nostrils. (Really, who deletes music?)
